==English==

===Noun===
'''[[shock]] [[site]]'''  (''plural:'' '''[[shock sites]]''')

# A [[website]] intended to be [[offensive]] or [[shock]]ing to most viewers, containing frightening and/or [[extreme]]ly [[distasteful]] and crude content of a [[pornographic]], [[scatological]], or [[grotesquely]] [[violent]] nature.  In most cases, it displays a particular picture most prominently; some shock sites also show animations or galleries of images, particularly shock images.

